Business Brief -- Anago Inc.:
   Mays Acquisition to Make
   An Offer for Firm's Shares
As reported, Tecnol, another Fort Worth maker of medical
supplies, earlier this month began a tender offer to acquire
200,000 Anago shares for the $7-a-share price, which would
give it control of more than 50% of Anago's stock. Tecnol
said at the time that it owned about 49% of Anago's 2.2
million shares, assuming conversion of its preferred shares
to common.